This paper discusses the detection of Denial of Service (DOS) attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also uses machine learning algorithms to detect the attacks, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the design of a system to detect the attacks, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
